<style>
.noscroll {
 overflow: hidden;
}

.hiddendiv {
 display: none;
 white-space: pre-wrap;
 min-height: 36px;
 min-width: 100px;
 font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
 font-size: 13px;
 overflow: hidden;
 padding: 5px;
 word-wrap: break-word;
}
</style>

<div id="[[Dev2elementNameTextarea]]Dev2HiddenAdjust" class="hiddendiv">[[Dev2RawData]]</div>

<script>
 /* start init */
 var extraHeight = 16; /* font size */
 var elm = $("#[[Dev2elementNameTextarea]]");
 var hiddenElm = $("#[[Dev2elementNameTextarea]]Dev2HiddenAdjust");
 /*hiddenElm = $(document.createElement("div")),
 content = "[[[[Dev2elementNameTextarea]]]]";
 $("body").append(hiddenElm);*/


 var baseW = elm.width();
 var wrapOn = "[[wrapText]]";
 elm.addClass("noscroll");
 hiddenElm.addClass("hiddendiv");

 /* only set width if in wrap mode */
 if(wrapOn == 'yes'){
 var hW = baseW - 35;
 if(hW < 0){
 hW = 100;
 }
 }else{
 hw = baseW - 40;
 }

 hiddenElm.css('width', hW); /* adjust width */
/* end init */


function [[menuID]](e){
 content = elm.val();
 content = content.replace(/\n/g, '<br/>');
 hiddenElm.html(content);

 var w = hiddenElm.width() * 2;

 if(w > baseW){
 if(wrapOn != 'yes'){
 elm.css('width', w);
 baseW = w*1.2;
 }
 }

 /* adjust on every enter pressed */
 try{
 if(e != null){
 var code = (e.keyCode ? e.keyCode : e.which);
 if(code == 13){
 var newH = hiddenElm.height() + extraHeight;
 hiddenElm.css('height', newH);
 content += "<br/>";
 }
 }
 }catch(err){}

 elm.css('height', hiddenElm.height()+extraHeight);
}
 /* bind to document load */
 $(function(){
 [[menuID]](null);
 });
 /* bind to key press */
 elm.bind('keyup', function(e) {
 [[menuID]](e);
 });

</script>
